</div>
<div>
<p class="text-label-md font-bold text-electric-blue uppercase">Cuándo</p>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Luces parpadeantes, disyuntores que saltan frecuentemente.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Card 2: Iluminación -->
<div class="service-card group relative bg-surface-subtle p-8 rounded-xl shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,51,102,0.06)] hover:shadow-xl transition-all scale-up">
<div class="accent-strip absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-0 bg-electric-blue transition-all rounded-t-xl"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-electric-blue text-4xl mb-6">lightbulb</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-deep-navy mb-4">Iluminación</h3>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div>
