<div class="space-y-4"><div><p class="text-label-md font-bold text-electric-blue">Incluye</p><p class="text-body-md">Conexiones eléctricas dedicadas para HVAC.</p></div></div>
</div>
<div class="service-card group relative bg-surface-subtle p-8 rounded-xl shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,51,102,0.06)] scale-up">
<div class="accent-strip absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-0 bg-electric-blue transition-all rounded-t-xl"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-electric-blue text-4xl mb-6">security</span>
